other_tests.findings: Distended gallbladder without pericholecystic fluid or gallbladder wall edema; normal liver, spleen, kidneys, adrenals, pancreas, small and large bowel; fat-containing umbilical hernia; mild atherosclerotic calcifications in abdominal aorta; bilateral fat-containing inguinal hernias; grade 1 anterolisthesis of L5 on S1.
